{"tid":704150,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Note 9 變大了!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-06-16T08:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T12:38:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b66a6ae40692e8c1b9ffd2f75d3ba28b5d25c39a","tid":704150,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"自從 Galaxy Note 7 爆炸事件後，Samsung 對於電池和快充就一直持保守態度。而華為在快充技術方面反之遙遙領先，即使其他廠早就在使用 QC 3.0 技術。面對日漸強勢的廠，Samsung 不得不在這些方面做出改變。<br />\n<br />\n日前有消息稱，Samsung 將於8月9日在紐約正式發布年度旗艦 Galaxy Note 9 。而今天早晨，微博博主@i冰宇宙透露了 Note 9 將迎來兩大新特性，一個是電池容量確認為 4000mAh ，之前有傳聞稱該機電池容量為3850mAh，看來經過堆疊式主板設計和橫向指紋佈局後，Samsung 為 Note 9 的內部騰出了更大容量的電池。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面是關於充電器的消息，據悉，該充電器是 Samsung 第六代無線充電器，型號為EP-N6100 ，12V/2.1A 充電功率為25.2W ，遠超 Samsung 現有的最高15W。並且由於近兩年 Samsung 有線和無線快充的規格是完全一致的，所以這一規格也很有可能應用於未來 Samsung 旗艦機的有線充電上，Note 9 機會很大。<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/06/15/galaxy-note-9-battery-up-to-4000mah/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2Fgalaxy-note-9-battery-up-to-4000mah%2F&d=pf22FSXlZHl%2F3nQR5BVjv26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=275e46f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/06/15/galaxy-note-9-battery-up-to-4000mah/</a>"},{"pid":"52d7d4bfa7059bf5089bfc94b5076feee08a961f","tid":704150,"uid":68320,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"碌鳩識變大<br />\n抵玩"},{"pid":"bb8fca8433bd732d64a6de7266e00dd57ea7154e","tid":704150,"uid":164092,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52d7d4bfa7059bf5089bfc94b5076feee08a961f","tid":704150,"uid":68320,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"碌鳩識變大<br />\n抵玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540c7cb251d902d49547bd1b4b4ba1f943094172","tid":704150,"uid":92